also_known_as: Uchikawa Ai / 内川 藍維
Kamata Chitose / 鎌田 千歳
biography:
Ai Uchikawa is a Japanese voice actress, currently affiliated with Sigma 7. She's also known under her real and former stagename Yuka Uchikawa.

Kamata Chitose is a guise of Uchikawa Ai for adult games and anime.
